  "Description": {
    "English": "A handful of <span class=\"name name-special\">glassy orbs</span>, once owned by Specialist Polo. Their pearlescent surface does not reflect the world around them, offering instead a mirror to different reality.<br><br>A valuable and exotic component, this would be of great use to Iteration: Tethys in <span class=\"name name-technology\">repairing</span> the shattered Drone.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一捧<span class=\"name name-special\">玻璃质地的圆球</span>，曾经属于保罗专家。玻璃珠的闪亮外层并不会反射周围的世界，而是会显现出另一个维度的镜像画面。<br><br>极其珍贵的异星构件，能够帮助迭代：特提斯<span class=\"name name-technology\">修复</span>破碎的无人机。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一些<span class=\"name name-special\">玻璃球</span>，曾經是專家波羅的物品。散發珠光的表面不會反射周遭的世界，而是成為了不同現實的鏡子。<br><br>一種珍貴又奇特的外星元件，在迭代：忒堤斯<span class=\"name name-technology\">修理</span>破碎的無人機時，會十分有用。"
  },
